---
title: Garlic-Herb Beef & Crumbly Cheese with Roast Veggie Couscous & Romesco Sauce
description: Quickly cooked beef strips meld together wonderfully with smokey romesco sauce in this Spanish-inspired dish. Make it a meal
with fluffy couscous and crumbly cheese, and now you’ve got yourself a fusion of textures and flavours you simply can’t resist!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/garlic-herb-beef-crumbly-cheese-58eae635.jpg
